yingyinNormal.en: You need to tell your guys to stop going out to the damn pile if they're injured. I keep patching up the same damn guys.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的人如果有受伤的，你得告诉他们不能再去倒霉的房子那。我不停地给同一拨人清创。

yingyinNormal.en: No one was killed, but more than a thousand people were injured.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没人被杀死，但超过1000人受伤。

yingyinNormal.en: She's injured. Any results would be unclear. You can get rid of her.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她受伤了，测试结果将受影响，你来处理她。

yingyinNormal.en: My purpose is to heal, the sick and injured. Baymax, open your access port.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的功能是去疗伤，帮助病号和伤员，大白，打开你的插卡器。

yingyinNormal.en: He was injured at 7:00. Went to the emergency room and was released at 7:30.
yingyinNormal.zh: 7点受伤，去了急诊室，7点30分离开。

yingyinNormal.en: My husband? It's my son. Your son. Will was injured in a road accident two years ago.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我丈夫？是我儿子。您的儿子。威尔两年前在一场车祸中受了伤。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, that's right. They stuck their noses into other people's worlds and got fatally injured.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，我想起来了.那帮老家伙去管别人的闲事，结果死的死伤的伤。

yingyinNormal.en: Anything. The whole point is to look like they're gagging you, that you are the injured party.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么都行。就是要看起来他们禁止了你说话，你是受害者。

yingyinNormal.en: No one has ever died or been injured in any car accident caused by my t-port. That would be news to my client.
yingyinNormal.zh: 目前还没有关于我的便携科技的伤亡事故记录。可这对于我的委托人来说却是全新的。
